Escape room "Abduction" by Get Out Starkville in Starkville
review: Awesome experience! Our game moderators were really helpful and fun. We did the Professor room and the Abduction and they were both super fun and exciting! Highly recommend this to anyone looking to have a lot of fun!

room_title: Escape room "Abduction" by Get Out Starkville in Starkville
review: I went with my brothers and sisters and we had a blast! They have it set up amazing. You have 3 hints you can get if you choose. We did the Abduction room and I recommend this if you are expecting a trip to Starkville!

room_title: Escape room "Abduction" by Get Out Starkville in Starkville
review: My family of 6 had a great time in the Abduction Room! Very challenging and a little bit creepy, in a good way. Will be going back next month for my birthday.
